---
import PageLayout from '@/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import { Badge } from '@/components/ui/badge';
---

<PageLayout title="Terms & Conditions" description="Terms of service for Unleft.">
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 px-4">
      <Badge className="mb-6 bg-accent-primary/10 text-accent-glow border-none mx-auto w-fit">Legal & Safety</Badge>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-8 tracking-tighter" style={{ fontFamily: "'Bruno Ace SC', sans-serif" }}>
        Terms & <span class="text-accent-primary">Conditions</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-text-secondary leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        The legal framework that governs our professional commitment to your projects.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-8 text-sm font-mono text-accent-glow uppercase tracking-widest">Last updated: March 2026</p>
    </div>

    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-accent-primary/5 rounded-3xl blur-3xl opacity-50"></div>
      <div class="relative rounded-2xl border border-[#2D2D44] bg-[#0A0A0F]/60 p-8 md:p-12 backdrop-blur-sm shadow-2xl">
        <div class="prose prose-invert prose-headings:font-heading prose-headings:text-text-primary prose-p:text-text-secondary prose-li:text-text-secondary prose-a:text-accent-glow max-w-none prose-h2:text-2xl prose-h2:mt-12 prose-h2:mb-6">
          <h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p>By accessing and using the Unleft website (Unleft.space), you accept and agree to be bound by these terms and conditions.</p>
      
          <h2>2. Services</h2>
          <p>Unleft provides software development services including web development, game development, custom software, and AI-based systems. All project scopes, timelines, and pricing are agreed upon separately via project proposals.</p>
      
          <h2>3. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p>All content on this website, including text, graphics, logos, and code, is the property of Unleft unless otherwise stated. Client deliverables are transferred upon full payment as defined in individual contracts.</p>
      
          <h2>4. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>Unleft shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from the use of our website or services.</p>
      
          <h2>5. Payment Terms</h2>
          <p>Payment terms, milestones, and refund policies are defined on a per-project basis in individual service agreements.</p>
      
          <h2>6. Modifications</h2>
          <p>We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.</p>
      
          <h2>7. Contact</h2>
          <p>Questions about these terms can be directed to <a href="mailto:hello@Unleft.space">hello@Unleft.space</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
